title: Ep - 21 - The Bachelor’s Melissa Rycroft Strickland
description:
Melissa Rycroft Strickland explains what happened during The Bachelor’s most infamous episode of After The Rose Ceremony when Jason Mesnick admitted he was in love with the runner-up Molly. She also gives insight into filming Dancing With The Stars and Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team.
